==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Drawloom
<hw>Draw"loom`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A kind
of loom used in weaving figured patterns; -- called also
<altname>drawboy</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A species of damask made on the drawloom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drawn</ent>⟦br⟧
